{{Actor| | type = Armor | name = Silver shield | class = SilverShield | game = Heretic | doomednum = 85 | spawnid = 68 | spawnname = T_SHIELD1 }}[[Classes]]: [[Classes:Inventory|Inventory]]&rarr;[[Classes:Armor|Armor]]&rarr;[[Classes:BasicArmorPickup|BasicArmorPickup]]&rarr;<u>SilverShield</u>
The silver shield is the [[Heretic]] equivalent to the [[Classes:GreenArmor|green armor]] in [[Doom]], granting 100% armor to the player. However, the shield absorbs a higher percentage (50%) of damage per attack than its Doom counterpart.
